title: 266 - Another Man's Salmon
description: Are opportunities given or created? In today’s episode, the guys wrestle with this concept and settle on the fact that regardless of how the opportunity originated, what matters most is what we do with it. Through colorful stories (including one about salmon) and some good old fashioned advice, the guys implore us to always seek to be faithful to the opportunities we have and get the most out of them.
